c: 6
v: 25
t: "Nabiyow ama korosuk atu Qhuraan takriye waqdi, koo ankacsa mari keenit yan, ken lubbittet Sibaabi hayneeh ken aytiital Qilsa hayne ama Qhuraan yafhimeenih yaaxigeenimik, kulli astay Nabii Numm â tascassel yableenimih teetil mayaaminan, Nabiyow usun koo fanah yamaaten waqdi koo giddiyaanah, koroosite mari ama Qhuraan kalah tuhinna usuk awwalî mari yuktube hayyayyoona akke waytek iyyan"